Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我買了用來做聖誕禮物的毛線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我會給大家編織好多好多的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,裝扮成聖誕老人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就能從朋君房間的窗戶送達了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不用做到那種地步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因為父親再婚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,來了個奇怪的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:23.50,TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(582,233)}心跳♡7
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:23.50,TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\pos(688,331)\fad(500,0)}聖誕節、來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 茶發…水原君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,被姐姐稍微扁了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,琉璃琉璃姐姐真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,茶發…水原君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有被姐姐扁過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有受過愛的鞭撻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.18,0:00:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可憐的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好疲倦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 藤咲同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,今年的聖誕節有什麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今年在家和家人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,藤咲同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,聖誕節有什麼預定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這次的聖誕聚會 要邀請藤咲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,反正她要和男生玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.59,0:01:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,聖誕老人會送同性的支持率嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,來多買點毛線的時候竟然能遇到朋君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好 需要包裝下是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}請稍等…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,包裝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,朋君的禮物被…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要給喜歡的女孩子的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,雖 雖然有點髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:01:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,表情好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,本來打算聖誕節再給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,既然本人已經拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,能 能收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次穿從朋君那裡收到的襪子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,過聖誕節 人多才開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
